EASTERN NORTH ATLANTIC.
SCOTLAND.
DNC 19.
1. HAZARDOUS OPERATIONS 1100Z TO 1900Z DAILY
   03 THRU 06 MAY IN AREA WITHIN 73 MILES OF
   56-59N 009-53W. VESSELS INTENDING TO
   ENTER AREA SHOULD CONTACT HEBRIDES RANGE
   CONTROL ON VHF CH 16 OR PHONE: 187 060 4449
   FOR ADVICE.
2. CANCEL THIS MSG 062000Z MAY 22.
